function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	actorClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_MONK_OUTSIDE)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorClone) then
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_MONK_02, id_Self, actorClone)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(actorClone, CONVO_MONK_02)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorClone, LOC_MONK_RUN, "NPC_WALK_Fast", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(actorClone, 0.5)
	end
	
end

	end
	
end
